{"tid":1645172,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人 記得我地已經無野可以輸","createTime":"2019-10-10T19:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T22:55:47.000Z","uid":58685,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"2e720894d34ab55584160d66e0e5c1df9777bcf2","tid":1645172,"uid":58685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:30:20.000Z","msg":"我睇完中大女義士 受盡咁多委屈之後到而家都訓唔到 喊都喊左幾次<br />\n 每睇一次就喊一次<br />\n但係香港人到而家呢場運動4個月就開始慢慢咁冷卻 <br />\n我求大家去到呢個時候 <br />\n千萬唔好因為慣左每日既新聞而慢慢麻目<br />\n 我地今次係唔輸得 <br />\n一輸就乜都無曬 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n求下 香港人 醒覺啦 唔好令到前線手足/和理非心灰意冷 今次輸左 我地所有真香港人 真係會一無所有 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3effce15223910b33d7e26d95a20805655c4b658","tid":1645172,"uid":58685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:31:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"933c4a548f9aa1fa5f1cc1b43fb932a0232364ac","tid":1645172,"uid":293816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:33:17.000Z","msg":"個心真係好痛完全瞓唔着"},{"pid":"57ab6863d4058074a7cd994e1bf7045546841c3e","tid":1645172,"uid":201141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:33:32.000Z","msg":"成日話唔好輸唔好輸 諗起點樣升級到武裝再同班拎槍既政權講數好過啦<br />\n無槍講咩都假 唔通真係期待班狗放低身gear同你打咩"},{"pid":"d977890e520cc01dde9959839964f20315c5b8e7","tid":1645172,"uid":58685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T19:33:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我求你地大家一齊守護我地既家"},{"pid":"d3ae54e23b5bff1343ebc6d024eec2864fe87647","tid":1645172,"uid":58685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"933c4a548f9aa1fa5f1cc1b43fb932a0232364ac","tid":1645172,"uid":293816,"like":0,"di